Petrovoll Dexö Multi ATF

  1. Products
  2. Petrovoll Dexö Multi ATF

Petrovöll Dexö Multi is a high performance, synthetic automotive transmission fluid for modern automatic gearboxes. It is formulated to have reduced viscosity using the most advanced additives and a special base oil composition made of HC synthetic oils and fully synthetic polyalpha-olefins (PAO).
